  <entry>
    <title>C++多线程基础 - 从零实现生产者-消费者模式</title>
    <link href="/2026/05/12/multithreading_basics/"/>
    <url>/2026/05/12/multithreading_basics/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p><strong>学习目标</strong>：掌握C++多线程编程核心概念，理解并实现经典的生产者-消费者模式.</p></blockquote><span id="more"></span><h2 id="📚-目录"><a href="#📚-目录" class="headerlink" title="📚 目录"></a>📚 目录</h2><ol><li><a href="#1-%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%9F">为什么需要多线程？</a></li><li><a href="#2-%E5%A4%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0">C++多线程基础实现</a></li><li><a href="#3-%E4%BA%92%E6%96%A5%E9%94%81%EF%BC%9A%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90">互斥锁：保护共享资源</a></li><li><a href="#4-%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%9A%E7%BA%BF%E7%A8%8B%E9%97%B4%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1">条件变量：线程间通信</a></li><li><a href="#5-%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E5%8F%8C%E7%BC%93%E5%86%B2%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0">实战：双缓冲队列实现</a></li><li><a href="#6-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88">常见陷阱与解决方案</a></li></ol><hr><h2 id="1-为什么需要多线程？"><a href="#1-为什么需要多线程？" class="headerlink" title="1. 为什么需要多线程？"></a>1. 为什么需要多线程？</h2><h3 id="场景引入"><a href="#场景引入" class="headerlink" title="场景引入"></a>场景引入</h3><p>想象你正在开发一个视频处理系统：</p><figure class="highlight erlang"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs erlang">❌ 单线程方案：<br>加载图像 → 处理图像 → 保存结果 → 加载下一张 → ...<br>     ↑ 大量时间浪费在IO等待上！<br><br>✅ 多线程方案：<br>加载线程：加载图像<span class="hljs-number">1</span> → 加载图像<span class="hljs-number">2</span> → 加载图像<span class="hljs-number">3</span> → ...<br>处理线程：          处理图像<span class="hljs-number">1</span> → 处理图像<span class="hljs-number">2</span> → 处理图像<span class="hljs-number">3</span> → ...<br>     ↑ IO和计算并行，效率提升<span class="hljs-number">3</span>-<span class="hljs-number">5</span>倍！<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="多线程的优势"><a href="#多线程的优势" class="headerlink" title="多线程的优势"></a>多线程的优势</h3><ul><li><strong>提高CPU利用率</strong>：IO等待时CPU可以执行其他任务</li><li><strong>响应性更好</strong>：UI线程不会被长时间操作阻塞</li><li><strong>充分利用多核</strong>：现代CPU通常有4-16个核心</li></ul><hr><h2 id="2-多线程基础实现"><a href="#2-多线程基础实现" class="headerlink" title="2. 多线程基础实现"></a>2. 多线程基础实现</h2><h3 id="2-1-创建线程"><a href="#2-1-创建线程" class="headerlink" title="2.1 创建线程"></a>2.1 创建线程</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;thread&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 方式1：普通函数</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">hello_function</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello from thread!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 方式2：Lambda表达式</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">auto</span> hello_lambda = []() &#123;<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Hello from lambda thread!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 方式3：成员函数</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Worker</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">do_work</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Working...&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 创建并启动线程</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t1</span><span class="hljs-params">(hello_function)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t2</span><span class="hljs-params">(hello_lambda)</span></span>;<br><br>    Worker worker;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t3</span><span class="hljs-params">(&amp;Worker::do_work, &amp;worker)</span></span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// ⚠️ 重要：必须join或detach</span><br>    t<span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();   <span class="hljs-comment">// 等待线程结束</span><br>    t<span class="hljs-number">2.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();<br>    t<span class="hljs-number">3.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-2-join-vs-detach"><a href="#2-2-join-vs-detach" class="headerlink" title="2.2 join vs detach"></a>2.2 join vs detach</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t</span><span class="hljs-params">([]()&#123;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-params"><span class="hljs-function">    <span class="hljs-comment">// 耗时操作</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-params"><span class="hljs-function">&#125;)</span></span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ join：主线程等待子线程完成</span><br>t.<span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 忘记join/detach会导致程序崩溃</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// t.~thread();  // std::terminate!</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ⚠️ detach：线程独立运行，无法再控制</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// t.detach();  // 谨慎使用！</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-3-RAII管理线程生命周期"><a href="#2-3-RAII管理线程生命周期" class="headerlink" title="2.3 RAII管理线程生命周期"></a>2.3 RAII管理线程生命周期</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">ThreadGuard</span> &#123;<br>    std::thread&amp; t_;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">explicit</span> <span class="hljs-title">ThreadGuard</span><span class="hljs-params">(std::thread&amp; t)</span> : t_(t) &#123;</span>&#125;<br>    ~<span class="hljs-built_in">ThreadGuard</span>() &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (t_.<span class="hljs-built_in">joinable</span>()) &#123;<br>            t_.<span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();  <span class="hljs-comment">// 自动join</span><br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">example</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t</span><span class="hljs-params">([]()&#123; <span class="hljs-comment">/* work */</span> &#125;)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">ThreadGuard <span class="hljs-title">guard</span><span class="hljs-params">(t)</span></span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 离开作用域时自动join</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 即使抛出异常也能安全清理</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="3-互斥锁：保护共享资源"><a href="#3-互斥锁：保护共享资源" class="headerlink" title="3. 互斥锁：保护共享资源"></a>3. 互斥锁：保护共享资源</h2><h3 id="3-1-数据竞争问题"><a href="#3-1-数据竞争问题" class="headerlink" title="3.1 数据竞争问题"></a>3.1 数据竞争问题</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;thread&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> shared_counter = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">increment</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="hljs-number">1000000</span>; ++i) &#123;<br>        shared_counter++;  <span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 非原子操作，导致数据竞争！</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t1</span><span class="hljs-params">(increment)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t2</span><span class="hljs-params">(increment)</span></span>;<br><br>    t<span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();<br>    t<span class="hljs-number">2.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();<br><br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Counter: &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; shared_counter &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 期望：2000000，实际：可能是1500000-2000000之间的任意值</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-2-使用mutex保护"><a href="#3-2-使用mutex保护" class="headerlink" title="3.2 使用mutex保护"></a>3.2 使用mutex保护</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;mutex&gt;</span></span><br><br>std::mutex counter_mutex;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> shared_counter = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">safe_increment</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="hljs-number">1000000</span>; ++i) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(counter_mutex)</span></span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 加锁</span><br>        shared_counter++;<br>    &#125;  <span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 自动解锁（RAII）</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-3-lock-guard-vs-unique-lock"><a href="#3-3-lock-guard-vs-unique-lock" class="headerlink" title="3.3 lock_guard vs unique_lock"></a>3.3 lock_guard vs unique_lock</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp">std::mutex mtx;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// lock_guard：简单场景，构造时加锁，析构时解锁</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 临界区代码</span><br>&#125;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 自动解锁</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// unique_lock：灵活，可以手动控制</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::unique_lock&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 临界区代码</span><br><br>    lock.<span class="hljs-built_in">unlock</span>();  <span class="hljs-comment">// 提前解锁</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 其他操作</span><br><br>    lock.<span class="hljs-built_in">lock</span>();    <span class="hljs-comment">// 再次加锁</span><br>&#125;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 自动解锁（如果还持有锁）</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-4-避免死锁"><a href="#3-4-避免死锁" class="headerlink" title="3.4 避免死锁"></a>3.4 避免死锁</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp">std::mutex mtx1, mtx2;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 可能导致死锁</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">thread_a</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock1</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx1)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock2</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx2)</span></span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 可能等待</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">thread_b</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock2</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx2)</span></span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 可能等待</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock1</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx1)</span></span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 使用std::scoped_lock同时锁定多个mutex</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">safe_thread_a</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::scoped_lock <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx1, mtx2)</span></span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 原子地锁定两个mutex</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 临界区</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="4-条件变量：线程间通信"><a href="#4-条件变量：线程间通信" class="headerlink" title="4. 条件变量：线程间通信"></a>4. 条件变量：线程间通信</h2><h3 id="4-1-为什么需要条件变量？"><a href="#4-1-为什么需要条件变量？" class="headerlink" title="4.1 为什么需要条件变量？"></a>4.1 为什么需要条件变量？</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 忙等待：浪费CPU</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (!data_ready) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 空转，占用100% CPU</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 条件变量：高效等待</span><br><span class="hljs-function">std::unique_lock&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx)</span></span>;<br>cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock, []&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> data_ready; &#125;);  <span class="hljs-comment">// 线程休眠，不占用CPU</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-2-基本用法"><a href="#4-2-基本用法" class="headerlink" title="4.2 基本用法"></a>4.2 基本用法</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;condition_variable&gt;</span></span><br><br>std::mutex mtx;<br>std::condition_variable cv;<br><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> data_ready = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> shared_data = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 生产者线程</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">producer</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    std::this_thread::<span class="hljs-built_in">sleep_for</span>(std::chrono::<span class="hljs-built_in">seconds</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>));<br><br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx)</span></span>;<br>        shared_data = <span class="hljs-number">42</span>;<br>        data_ready = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">notify_one</span>();  <span class="hljs-comment">// 通知一个等待的线程</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 消费者线程</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">consumer</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::unique_lock&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx)</span></span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 等待直到data_ready为true</span><br>    cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock, []&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> data_ready; &#125;);<br><br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Received: &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; shared_data &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-3-虚假唤醒（Spurious-Wakeup）"><a href="#4-3-虚假唤醒（Spurious-Wakeup）" class="headerlink" title="4.3 虚假唤醒（Spurious Wakeup）"></a>4.3 虚假唤醒（Spurious Wakeup）</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 错误：没有使用predicate</span><br>cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock);  <span class="hljs-comment">// 可能被虚假唤醒！</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 正确：总是使用predicate</span><br>cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock, []&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> condition; &#125;);<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 等价于：</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (!condition) &#123;<br>    cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-4-notify-one-vs-notify-all"><a href="#4-4-notify-one-vs-notify-all" class="headerlink" title="4.4 notify_one vs notify_all"></a>4.4 notify_one vs notify_all</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp">cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">notify_one</span>();   <span class="hljs-comment">// 唤醒一个等待线程（效率高）</span><br>cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">notify_all</span>();   <span class="hljs-comment">// 唤醒所有等待线程（适用于多个消费者）</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="5-实战：双缓冲队列实现"><a href="#5-实战：双缓冲队列实现" class="headerlink" title="5. 实战：双缓冲队列实现"></a>5. 实战：双缓冲队列实现</h2><h3 id="5-1-设计思路"><a href="#5-1-设计思路" class="headerlink" title="5.1 设计思路"></a>5.1 设计思路</h3><figure class="highlight scss"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs scss">┌─────────────┐         ┌──────────────┐<br>│ 加载线程     │         │ 读取线程      │<br>│ (Producer)  │         │ (Consumer)   │<br>└──────┬──────┘         └──────┬───────┘<br>       │                       │<br>       ▼                       │<br>  write_buffer                 │<br>       │                       │<br>       │  <span class="hljs-built_in">swapBuffers</span>()        │<br>       ├──────────────────────►│<br>                               ▼<br>                          read_buffer<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-2-核心数据结构"><a href="#5-2-核心数据结构" class="headerlink" title="5.2 核心数据结构"></a>5.2 核心数据结构</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T&gt;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">DoubleBuffer</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">private</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 双缓冲区</span><br>    std::vector&lt;T&gt; write_buffer_;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 加载线程写入</span><br>    std::vector&lt;T&gt; read_buffer_;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 读取线程读取</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 同步机制</span><br>    std::mutex write_mutex_;<br>    std::mutex swap_mutex_;<br>    std::condition_variable write_cv_;<br>    std::condition_variable read_cv_;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 状态标志</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">bool</span> is_ready_to_swap_ = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">bool</span> is_stop_requested_ = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 后台线程</span><br>    std::shared_ptr&lt;std::thread&gt; worker_thread_;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 启动后台加载</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">start</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        worker_thread_ = std::<span class="hljs-built_in">make_shared</span>&lt;std::thread&gt;(<br>            &amp;DoubleBuffer::loadWorker, <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 停止并清理</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">stop</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>        &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(write_mutex_)</span></span>;<br>            is_stop_requested_ = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        write_cv_.<span class="hljs-built_in">notify_all</span>();<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (worker_thread_ &amp;&amp; worker_thread_-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">joinable</span>()) &#123;<br>            worker_thread_-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    ~<span class="hljs-built_in">DoubleBuffer</span>() &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">stop</span>();  <span class="hljs-comment">// RAII：自动清理</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-3-后台加载线程"><a href="#5-3-后台加载线程" class="headerlink" title="5.3 后台加载线程"></a>5.3 后台加载线程</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">loadWorker</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (!is_stop_requested_) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 1. 检查是否需要等待swap</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (is_ready_to_swap_) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-function">std::unique_lock&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(write_mutex_)</span></span>;<br>            write_cv_.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock, [<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>]&#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> !is_ready_to_swap_ || is_stop_requested_;<br>            &#125;);<br>        &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-comment">// 2. 加载数据到write_buffer</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-built_in">loadDataToWriteBuffer</span>();<br><br>                <span class="hljs-comment">// 3. 标记为可交换</span><br>                &#123;<br>                    <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(swap_mutex_)</span></span>;<br>                    is_ready_to_swap_ = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>                &#125;<br>                read_cv_.<span class="hljs-built_in">notify_all</span>();  <span class="hljs-comment">// 通知读取线程</span><br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-built_in">catch</span> (...) &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-comment">// 异常处理</span><br>                <span class="hljs-built_in">handleException</span>();<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-4-缓冲区交换"><a href="#5-4-缓冲区交换" class="headerlink" title="5.4 缓冲区交换"></a>5.4 缓冲区交换</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title">swapBuffers</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!is_ready_to_swap_) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// O(1)复杂度交换指针</span><br>    read_buffer_.<span class="hljs-built_in">swap</span>(write_buffer_);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 重置状态</span><br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(write_mutex_)</span></span>;<br>        is_ready_to_swap_ = <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    write_cv_.<span class="hljs-built_in">notify_all</span>();  <span class="hljs-comment">// 通知加载线程继续工作</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-5-读取数据"><a href="#5-5-读取数据" class="headerlink" title="5.5 读取数据"></a>5.5 读取数据</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title">readNext</span><span class="hljs-params">(T&amp; data)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 1. 如果read_buffer为空，等待</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (read_buffer_.<span class="hljs-built_in">empty</span>()) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-function">std::unique_lock&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(swap_mutex_)</span></span>;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 带超时的等待</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">bool</span> notified = read_cv_.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait_for</span>(<br>            lock,<br>            std::chrono::<span class="hljs-built_in">seconds</span>(<span class="hljs-number">60</span>),<br>            [<span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>]&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> is_ready_to_swap_ || is_stop_requested_; &#125;<br>        );<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!notified || !is_ready_to_swap_) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 超时或停止</span><br>        &#125;<br><br>        lock.<span class="hljs-built_in">unlock</span>();<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">swapBuffers</span>();<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 2. 从read_buffer读取</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!read_buffer_.<span class="hljs-built_in">empty</span>()) &#123;<br>        data = read_buffer_.<span class="hljs-built_in">back</span>();<br>        read_buffer_.<span class="hljs-built_in">pop_back</span>();<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">false</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="6-常见陷阱与解决方案"><a href="#6-常见陷阱与解决方案" class="headerlink" title="6. 常见陷阱与解决方案"></a>6. 常见陷阱与解决方案</h2><h3 id="6-1-忘记join线程"><a href="#6-1-忘记join线程" class="headerlink" title="6.1 忘记join线程"></a>6.1 忘记join线程</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 危险！</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">bad_example</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t</span><span class="hljs-params">([]()&#123; <span class="hljs-comment">/* work */</span> &#125;)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 忘记join，程序退出时std::terminate</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 正确</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">good_example</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::thread <span class="hljs-title">t</span><span class="hljs-params">([]()&#123; <span class="hljs-comment">/* work */</span> &#125;)</span></span>;<br>    t.<span class="hljs-built_in">join</span>();  <span class="hljs-comment">// 或使用RAII包装</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-2-锁粒度过大"><a href="#6-2-锁粒度过大" class="headerlink" title="6.2 锁粒度过大"></a>6.2 锁粒度过大</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 持锁时进行IO操作</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">auto</span> data = <span class="hljs-built_in">loadFromFile</span>();  <span class="hljs-comment">// 慢！其他线程被阻塞</span><br>    buffer.<span class="hljs-built_in">push</span>(data);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 缩小锁范围</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">auto</span> data = <span class="hljs-built_in">loadFromFile</span>();  <span class="hljs-comment">// 无锁IO</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function">std::lock_guard&lt;std::mutex&gt; <span class="hljs-title">lock</span><span class="hljs-params">(mtx)</span></span>;<br>    buffer.<span class="hljs-built_in">push</span>(data);  <span class="hljs-comment">// 快速操作</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-3-条件变量误用"><a href="#6-3-条件变量误用" class="headerlink" title="6.3 条件变量误用"></a>6.3 条件变量误用</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 没有检查条件就wait</span><br>cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock);<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 使用if而不是while</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!condition) &#123;<br>    cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 总是使用predicate</span><br>cv.<span class="hljs-built_in">wait</span>(lock, []&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> condition; &#125;);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-4-跨线程异常丢失"><a href="#6-4-跨线程异常丢失" class="headerlink" title="6.4 跨线程异常丢失"></a>6.4 跨线程异常丢失</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">// ❌ 异常在工作线程中被吞掉</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">worker</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">doWork</span>();<br>    &#125; <span class="hljs-built_in">catch</span> (...) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 异常被忽略！</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// ✅ 使用exception_ptr传递</span><br>std::exception_ptr exception_ptr_;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">worker</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">doWork</span>();<br>    &#125; <span class="hljs-built_in">catch</span> (...) &#123;<br>        exception_ptr_ = std::<span class="hljs-built_in">current_exception</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">checkException</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (exception_ptr_) &#123;<br>        std::<span class="hljs-built_in">rethrow_exception</span>(exception_ptr_);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="📖-延伸阅读"><a href="#📖-延伸阅读" class="headerlink" title="📖 延伸阅读"></a>📖 延伸阅读</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.manning.com/books/c-plus-plus-concurrency-in-action-second-edition">C++ Concurrency in Action</a></li><li><a href="https://en.cppreference.com/w/cpp/thread">cppreference.com - Thread support library</a></li><li><a href="https://www.aristeia.com/ECMME.html">Effective Modern C++ - Item 35-40</a></li></ul><hr><h2 id="💡-总结"><a href="#💡-总结" class="headerlink" title="💡 总结"></a>💡 总结</h2><p>通过本文学习如下：</p><p>✅ C++线程的基本创建和管理<br>✅ 互斥锁的使用和死锁避免<br>✅ 条件变量的正确使用模式<br>✅ 生产者-消费者模式的完整实现<br>✅ 常见的多线程陷阱及解决方案  </p><hr>]]></content>
    
    
